{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people that were inside-- we were put in a barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were put in-- you know, we walked into this barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these-- the capos, they were our leaders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were in charge of the barrack, and they were so mean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we arrived to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Birkenau is where we got separated by the train, by the railroad train, and-- and we marched down one road and my parents and my-- I never saw my father and the-- the boys after that.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somebody said they went on a truck, you know, they'll be OK, before we realized where that truck went.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that made me feel a little bit better before we really found out what really happened to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't find out for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- when we came into the camp and they brought me in with the group to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's C in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was-- they put us into this barrack, and I think it was barrack number 24.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I know I was at one time or another in a barrack 24, because I was in several during my stay there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I think the first one could have been 24.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that wasn't even important, because it wasn't much we could have done about it to change it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when they opened the doors to the barrack, they told us that 10 each, 10 is to go into the bunk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were three-story wooden bunks in the barrack with a brick thing going in the middle from one end of the barrack to the other, looking like a large brick bench, which was supposed to be a stove to keep the barrack warm.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, they never heated the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
